<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="mathml.xsl"?><html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" /><title>gluQuadricOrientation</title><meta name="generator" content="DocBook XSL Stylesheets V1.69.1" /></head><body><div class="refentry" lang="en" xml:lang="en"><a id="gluQuadricOrientation"></a><div class="titlepage"></div><div class="refnamediv"><h2>Name</h2><p>gluQuadricOrientation — specify inside/outside orientation for quadrics</p></div><div class="refsynopsisdiv"><h2>C Specification</h2><div class="funcsynopsis"><table border="0" summary="Function synopsis" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="padding-bottom: 1em"><tr><td><code class="funcdef"> void <b class="fsfunc">gluQuadricOrientation</b>(</code></td><td><var class="pdparam">quad</var>, </td><td> </td></tr><tr><td> </td><td><var class="pdparam">orientation</var><code>)</code>;</td><td> </td></tr></table><table border="0" summary="Function argument synopsis" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td> GLUquadric*  </td><td><var class="pdparam">quad</var>;</td></tr><tr><td> GLenum  </td><td><var class="pdparam">orientation</var>;</td></tr></table></div></div><div class="refsect1" lang="en" xml:lang="en"><a id="id4781738"></a><h2>PARAMETERS</h2><div class="variablelist"><dl><dt><span class="term"><em class="parameter"><code>quad</code></em></span></dt><dd><p>
                    Specifies the quadrics object (created with <span class="citerefentry"><span class="refentrytitle">gluNewQuadric</span></span>).
                </p></dd><dt><span class="term"><em class="parameter"><code>orientation</code></em></span></dt><dd><p>
                    Specifies the desired orientation. Valid values are
                    <code class="constant">GLU_OUTSIDE</code> and
                    <code class="constant">GLU_INSIDE</code>.
                </p></dd></dl></div></div><div class="refsect1" lang="en" xml:lang="en"><a id="id4781661"></a><h2>DESCRIPTION</h2><p>
            <code class="function">gluQuadricOrientation</code> specifies what kind of orientation is desired for quadrics rendered 
            with <em class="parameter"><code>quad</code></em>. The <em class="parameter"><code>orientation</code></em> values are as follows:
        </p><div class="variablelist"><dl><dt><span class="term"><code class="constant">GLU_OUTSIDE</code> </span></dt><dd><p>
                        Quadrics are drawn with normals pointing outward (the initial value).
                    </p></dd><dt><span class="term"><code class="constant">GLU_INSIDE</code> </span></dt><dd><p>
                        Quadrics are drawn with normals pointing inward.
                    </p></dd></dl></div><p>
            Note that the interpretation of <span class="emphasis"><em>outward</em></span> and <span class="emphasis"><em>inward</em></span> depends on the
            quadric being drawn.
        </p></div><div class="refsect1" lang="en" xml:lang="en"><a id="id4768290"></a><h2>SEE ALSO</h2><p>
            <span class="citerefentry"><span class="refentrytitle">gluNewQuadric</span></span>,
            <span class="citerefentry"><span class="refentrytitle">gluQuadricDrawStyle</span></span>,
            <span class="citerefentry"><span class="refentrytitle">gluQuadricNormals</span></span>,
            <span class="citerefentry"><span class="refentrytitle">gluQuadricTexture</span></span>
        </p></div><div class="refsect1" lang="en" xml:lang="en"><a id="id4768319"></a><h2>COPYRIGHT</h2><p>
